{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>The Spiral</i> is a first-person roguelike dungeon crawler. Explore the dungeon, find tools for your survival, and try to escape with your life.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Descend into Darkness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore an infinite dungeon with randomized layouts, items, and enemies. No two playthroughs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/extras/explore.gif?t=1739380200\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find Powerful Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make use of the dungeon's bounty to survive. Simple farming tools, legendary weapons, curious potions, and enchanted charms are all at your disposal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/extras/loot.gif?t=1739380200\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight for Your Life</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are not alone. Monsters, nightmares, and other desperate wanderers like you all call the dungeon home. Kill them before they kill you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/extras/fight.gif?t=1739380200\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739380200","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/page.bg.jpg?t=1739380200","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/7f2375480b2f0487eddc195c96c3bb8af662ffbc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739380200","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577020/7f2375480b2f0487eddc195c96c3bb8af662ffbc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739380200","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full con